  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/7b2abf45534923325fc62b89af71574a.avif?t=1773676525\" width=1024 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Stoic; a short yet challenging platforming game with precise physics controls and punishing level building. In Stoic, you control an oddly spherical boulder with the objective of finding purpose, whether that be climbing an insurmountable mountain, or just biding your time enjoying the scenery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stoic loosely follows the story of Zeno of Citium, a man widely renowned as the founder of the Stoic school of philosophy. After surviving a terrible shipwreck on your wealthy merchant ship, you must now find purpose after becoming a sluggish and cumbersome boulder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/02c25382e25828dc050987df547f9fe9.avif?t=1773676525\" width=1024 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/806fc149dda8128f11f62a826de320c1.gif?t=1773676525\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/806fc149dda8128f11f62a826de320c1.poster.avif?t=1773676525\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More of an achievement hunter? Stoic has a total of 9 unlockable skins, with some featuring moments from Zeno's life or remembering his legacy. Can you find them all?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/7b2abf45534923325fc62b89af71574a.avif?t=1773676525\" width=1024 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Stoic; a short yet challenging platforming game with precise physics controls and punishing level building. In Stoic, you control an oddly spherical boulder with the objective of finding purpose, whether that be climbing an insurmountable mountain, or just biding your time enjoying the scenery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stoic loosely follows the story of Zeno of Citium, a man widely renowned as the founder of the Stoic school of philosophy. After surviving a terrible shipwreck on your wealthy merchant ship, you must now find purpose after becoming a sluggish and cumbersome boulder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/02c25382e25828dc050987df547f9fe9.avif?t=1773676525\" width=1024 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/806fc149dda8128f11f62a826de320c1.gif?t=1773676525\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4329640/extras/806fc149dda8128f11f62a826de320c1.poster.avif?t=1773676525\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More of an achievement hunter? Stoic has a total of 9 unlockable skins, with some featuring moments from Zeno's life or remembering his legacy. Can you find them all?</p>",
